            <div xml:id="trans1" xml:lang="en" type="translation" xml:space="preserve">
<p>
† Theodoros, the weaver has paid from the account of his house-rent of the current 1st indiction four one-fourth one-sixteenth gold carats, total 4 ¼ 1⁄₁₆ gold carats only. On the 20th of the month Epeiph of the 1st indiction. † Through me, Marcus paraphe
</p>
